    {
      "id": "identity-flow-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 385,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Upload: setup-identity.sh, docker-compose.keycloak.yml, .setup-creds\n\n1. Set hostname + /etc/hosts           5. DNS records (A + PTR) + forwarder\n2. Install FreeIPA packages (dnf)       6. Create SPN HTTP/api + test users\n3. Configure firewalld                     (ldappasswd for permanent passwords)\n4. ipa-server-install (~15 min)         7. Install Docker\n                                        8. Start Keycloak (Docker Compose)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 208,
