    {
      "id": "api-flow-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 600,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "Upload: setup-api.sh, nginx-api.conf,\n        api-src.tar.gz, .setup-creds\n\n1. Hostname + DNS -> FreeIPA\n2. Install packages (ipa-client, nginx)\n3. ipa-client-install (domain join)\n4. ipa-getkeytab AFTER enrollment\n   (fixes KVNO mismatch!)\n5. Install .NET 8, build API\n6. systemd service + nginx + TLS",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
