    {
      "id": "ws-flow-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 480,
      "y": 600,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "Upload: setup-workstation.sh,\n        launcher-ui-src.tar.gz, .setup-creds\n\n1. Hostname + DNS -> FreeIPA\n2. Install packages (ipa-client)\n3. ipa-client-install (domain join)\n4. Node.js 20 + pnpm (PATH fix)\n5. Install GNOME + Electron deps\n6. Extract source, pnpm install, make\n7. Write API config (api.yaml)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
